    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1900-11-24T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1900-11-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="458"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d458">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Choate</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-11-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 24, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 434.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Referring to your instruction No. 482, dated the
                    1st instant, relating to the desire of the American friends of Mr. William
                    Smith, a prisoner at St. Helena, to procure his release, I have the honor to
                    report that by means of unofficial inquiries I have reliably ascertained that no
                    application for the discharge of any particular prisoner at St. Helena would be
                    entertained; that requests for the discharge of other prisoners similarly
                    situated, made by other nations, directly and officially, have been refused, and
                    that it would therefore not be expedient to present an application in his
                    case.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Joseph H. Choate.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
